    <lesson title='Lines, Line Segments, Rays'></lesson>
        <body>Lines: A line is a straight one-dimensional geometric object that extends infinitely in both directions.\n
            Line Segment: A line segment is a straight one-dimensional geometric object that has fixed starting and ending points.\n
            Ray: A ray is a straight one-dimensional geometric object that has a fixed starting point, but extends infinitely.\n
        </body>
